title: Google launches its first dedicated public transport app, but for New Delhi residents only
text: Google has launched a new transport navigation app specifically for New Delhi in India. Though Google Maps itself offers public transport and transit options in many cities around the world, Delhi Public Transport Offline represents Google’s first ever city-specific app for travelers. The Android -only app does exactly what its name suggests — directions and timetable […] »
